 Chair Powell is optimistic about the US economy's strength, acknowledging Bitcoin as 'like gold'. Economy is in good shape with Powell committed to maintaining its condition. Full story on Benzinga.com.","id":"85a5aaaa-46c8-4268-a7df-237c2f2e8e38","is_major":false,"source":"Benzinga","source_type":"news","summary":"During the New York Times DealBook Summit, Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell discussed the strength of the U.S. economy and mentioned Bitcoin. Powell stated that the economy is currently in excellent condition, being the envy of other major global economies. He expressed his commitment to maintaining this strong position throughout the remainder of his term. Powell highlighted that the U.S. economy is doing well and the monetary policy is on track. This information was shared during the event, and a more detailed report can be found on Benzinga.com.","tickers":[],"time":"00:28:55","timestamp":"2024-12-05T00:28:55Z","url":"https://www.benzinga.com/markets/cryptocurrency/24/12/42330125/fed-chair-powell-says-economy-remains-strong-bitcoin-is-like-gold-expert-weighs-in"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"crypto","date":"2024-12-05","headline":"Binance's BNB Token Hits All-Time High as Bitcoin and Ethereum Alts Swell","id":"a42b272a-2805-4834-91ef-737546f68dcd","is_major":false,"source":"Decrypt","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"00:15:36","timestamp":"2024-12-05T00:15:36Z","url":"https://decrypt.co/294936/binances-bnb-token-hits-all-time-high-as-bitcoin-and-ethereum-alts-swell"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"news","date":"2024-12-05","headline":"KIA WINS FIRST UK AWARD FOR PV5 VAN AHEAD OF LAUNCH IN 2025","id":"300e2003-eb7a-4250-bdf7-bb50863230dd","is_major":false,"source":"PR NewsWire","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":[],"time":"00:13:41","timestamp":"2024-12-05T00:13:41Z","url":"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/kia-wins-first-uk-award-for-pv5-van-ahead-of-launch-in-2025-302323247.html"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"securities","date":"2024-12-05","headline":"Nxera Pharma enrolls first insomnia patient in Phase 3 trial of daridorexant in South Korea, previously known as Sosei Group.","id":"561e5edd-0651-4766-9f63-eeec483d038e","is_major":false,"source":"GlobeNewswire","source_type":"news","summary":"On December 5, 2024, Nxera Pharma Co., Ltd. (previously Sosei Group or Sosei Heptares) based in Tokyo, Japan and Cambridge, UK, disclosed the commencement of a Phase 3 clinical study for their new dual orexin receptor antagonist, daridorexant, targeted at treating adult patients suffering from insomnia in South Korea. The company, listed as TSE 4565, marked the randomization of the initial participant in this trial, signifying a significant advancement in their research and development efforts for this innovative treatment.","tickers":["TSE"],"time":"00:07:43","timestamp":"2024-12-05T00:07:43Z","url":"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/12/05/2991987/0/en/Nxera-Pharma-Enrolls-First-Insomnia-Patient-in-its-Phase-3-Clinical-Trial-of-Daridorexant-in-South-Korea.html"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"securities","date":"2024-12-05","headline":"Bezos, former Trump opponent, hopeful for Trump's 2nd term. Sees a \"calmer\" Trump.","id":"43d1207e-0284-42bd-8b2d-8e96fcbd4ac0","is_major":true,"source":"NYT","source_type":"news","summary":"The founder of Amazon noted a change in demeanor in former President Donald J. Trump, describing him as appearing \"calmer\" as he prepares to re-enter the White House.","tickers":[],"time":"00:05:38","timestamp":"2024-12-05T00:05:38Z","url":"https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/04/business/dealbook/jeff-bezos-trump-amazon-washington-post.html"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"news","date":"2024-12-05","headline":"Scholarship offers up to $20,000 for regenerative land management education for farmers and ranchers.","id":"c3c47665-67ad-44d4-adee-9610f1cc8be1","is_major":false,"source":"PR NewsWire","source_type":"news","summary":"ARDMORE, Okla. - Noble Research Institute has announced a scholarship opportunity for their 2025 online and in-person courses. Sponsored by Powerflex Supply and administered by the National Grazing Lands Coalition, the scholarship will offer up to $20,000 in registration assistance. This initiative aims to support individuals seeking to further their education in the agricultural sector.","tickers":[],"time":"00:03:38","timestamp":"2024-12-05T00:03:38Z","url":"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/land--legacy-scholarship-offers-farmers-and-ranchers-support-in-gaining-regenerative-land-and-business-management-education-302322260.html"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"securities","date":"2024-12-04","headline":"Woodside contracts Bechtel for Louisiana LNG development of 3 train, 16.5M tonnes/year; site work to continue under LNTP.","id":"46d61426-9758-4ac1-b0ec-fc1471119286","is_major":false,"source":"Business Wire","source_type":"news","summary":"In Perth, Australia, Woodside has entered into a new lump sum turnkey EPC agreement with Bechtel for the establishment of the three train 16.5 million tonnes per annum foundation project of Louisiana LNG. Bechtel, which has been involved on-site since the acquisition, will persist with their work under a limited notice to proceed (LNTP) that has been implemented in accordance with the adjusted EPC contract. The LNTP facilitates the ongoing construction at the site and entails dedication to specific key matters.","tickers":[],"time":"23:59:47","timestamp":"2024-12-04T23:59:47Z","url":"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20241204245574/en/Woodside-Signs-Agreement-for-Louisiana-LNG/?feedref=JjAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-YKT6SDyMw5Lye4ovXwHmkqD8R-QU5o2AvY8bhI9uvWSD8DYIYv4TIC1g1u0AKcacnnViVjtb72bOP4-4nHK5idAXrgr_e1ZUbxvK6BY66Xm"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"news","date":"2024-12-04","headline":"SmallRig Awards launches Global Filmmaker Talk series with 2024 Cannes Best Director Miguel Gomes in LA, showcasing Grand Tour.","id":"